(31, 'FC Helsingor vs FC Fredericia', NULL, '<p>FC Helsingor face&nbsp;FC Fredericia in the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://football-today.co.uk/leagues/Denmark/Viasat_Divisionen\">Viasat Divisionen</a>&nbsp;and has the potential to be a great watch. FC Helsingor finished 4th in the league last season meanwhile FC Fredercia finished 5th. This season both FC Helsingor and FC Fredericia are doing better, infact these tams are levelled on points with eachother,&nbsp;&nbsp;FC Helsingor are 2nd whilst FC Fredericia are 4th. These teams are just 2 points behind 1st place ,so a win for either one of these teams will take them to top of the league.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Past meetings&nbsp;</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>These teams have faced each other four times in this calendear year already, with FC Helsingor winning 3 of them and FC Fredericia winning just 1. In the last match we witnessed 6 goals with FC helsingor winning 2-4 away from home.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://football-today.co.uk/uploads/fc1a310e5c032d5a9766ba7da94f4dbf.png\" style=\"height:342px; width:300px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Team Statistics&nbsp;</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>FC Helsingor </strong>-&nbsp;FC Helsingor are 2nd in the league and have lost just 1 game this season and that was away from home. FC Helsingor have managed to score a whooping 14 goals from 6 home matches this season, that works out 2.3 goals a game whilst conceding 8 which is 1.3 goals. In total FC Helsingor have scored 31 goals from 14 matches which is 2.2 goals per game, pretty impressive for sure! But FC Helsingor have conceded 16 goals all together which works out 1.1 goals a game. The downfall to FC Helsingor is the amount of matches they have drawn. In total FC Helsingor have won 8 drawn 5 lost 1.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>FC Fredericia </strong>- FC Fredericia are 4th in the league losing 3 matches from 14 matches. FC Fredericia also enjoy scoring goals they&#39;ve scored 29 goals so far this season with 14 of them goals coming away from home, this works out as 2.0 away goals but despite scoring more away gooals, FC Fredericia also concede more goals away. So far this season they have conceded 10 goals which works out 1.4 goals a game. Overall FC Fredericia have won 9 matches this season which is joint first, drawing 2 and losing 3 matches. Just 1 of the defeats have came away from home.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Our predictions&nbsp;</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>This game is going to be very close, and it&#39;s very very hard to call a winner. Our prediction tool have given FC Helsingor a 55.2% chance of winning the match and we agree with this, we make them slights favorties. Looking at firepower these sides have, i think we will see goals in this one. <strong>Both teams to score </strong>is my first tip,&nbsp;im very confident with this. I think we will also see goals in both halves. Potentially <strong>Both teams to score in both halves </strong>might be worth a punt.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Score prediction 3-2</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '0dcd32d6f3ea23ba546d075d19d6807e.JPEG', '', 0, 0, NULL, '2021-11-07 14:15:21', '2023-01-04 10:20:21', 0),
(34, 'FC Eindhoven vs Dordrecht  13-11-21', NULL, '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>FC Eindhoven face bottom of the league Dordrecht, this is set to be a match full off goals. This game ended 8-1 in 2019 and since then one of these teams have won 5-1 on three occasions! Read on to see all the important and useful team stats. We also have left our predictions on this game like always, is there a shock on the cards here?&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Team stats</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>FC Eindhoven -</strong> FC Eindhoven have been doing good this season, they sit&nbsp;6th in the league and a win would move them up to 3rd in the league. FC Einhoven have played&nbsp;6 home matches this season winning 4, drawing 1 and losing 1. Einhoven score on average 1.8 home goals per game whilst conceding 1.2 goals.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Dordrecht - </strong>Dordrecht have been disappointing this season, they&#39;re bottom of the league winning just 2 games. One of the wins have been away from home, they also drawn 1 and lost 5 games away from home. Dordrecht concede on average 2.4 away goals whilst scoring 1.3 goals on average when playing away.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Head to head</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Eindhoven have a amazing record against Dordrecht, scoring an incredible 23 goals in their last 5 meetings!&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://football-today.co.uk/uploads/645e7f427a3ccba1a0d7c848f2fa8bb6.png\" style=\"height:554px; width:500px\" /></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Predictions -</strong> Our prediction tool have given Eindhoven a 71% chance of winning this match. Based on the stats and head to head i think this is accurate, at the moment you can get odds for Einhoven to win at&nbsp;1.6+, that would be my best tip for the match. I think this could be a potential both teams to score match, Dordrecht have scored in their last 5 meetings so despite their poor season they may grab their usual 1 goal..&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Score prediction 3-1&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://football-today.co.uk/articles/Excelsior_vs_Almere_city_fc\">We&#39;ve previewed tomorrows match between Excelsior and Almere city fc which you can read here</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'f4829ea3a028b7bd1e97103be300f4d5.JPEG', '', 0, 0, NULL, '2021-11-11 12:42:09', '2023-01-04 10:22:05', 0),
