(197, 'Value bets - Are they worth it', NULL, '<p>I had a couple of messages from people asking about value bets. So, I thought I would write an artlcle on them and hopefully this will help you understand value bets better.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>What is a value bet?&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>A value bet is considered a bet where you have the upperhand over the bookie this is reflected by&nbsp;you have better chance of winning than what the odds are set at.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&#39;Are they worh it?&#39;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you&#39;re doing them correctly, then yes they are 100% worth doing. But, you need to remember Value bets won&#39;t get you rich, it&#39;s a long term statedgy that can be profitble. I do Value bets often, and they do make me profit on most days. I haven&#39;t actually shared these bets yet, but if i get enough interest then maybe I will.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>T</p>', 'e4271b0c82b7ccf1ca4583b471bf877c.png', '', 0, 0, NULL, '2022-06-29 12:51:06', '2022-06-29 12:51:06', 0),
(198, 'How to make money by betting', NULL, '<p>I was talking to a follwerer the other guy about this question and we both raised some good points about this question, so i thought i&#39;d write an article so hopefully you can learn something new.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>How to make money by betting</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We&#39;ve already given you tips on how to be successful on betting which you can read here. Now we&#39;re going to tell you specificaly a method/plan that works and makes us money. We use many methods and have different plans that we follow, each of that makes us money long term. We don&#39;t win every bet we place and we have days where we will lose money. If anyone denies losing money then i woudln&#39;t trust them.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The method:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This method is pretty straightforward it&#39;s called &#39;value bets&#39;. Some of you will know what a value bet is others won&#39;t. Below we will tell you what a value bet is and how to make money by doing them.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>What is a value bet?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The way i would describe a value bet is where you have a better chance of winning than what the odds suggest. So essentially you have the upperhand over the bookies.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Here&#39;s an example of a value bet</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Odds on Barcelona to win are currently&nbsp;3.3. Based on the odds they have a 30% chance of winning the game.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You can work this out by 100/30 = 3.3</p>\r\n\r\n<p>However after doing your research and workout the actual probability&nbsp;you discover that infact Barcelona have a 40% chane of winning.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>100 divide by 40 = <strong>2.5&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>2.5 reflects what the odds should be but on the bookies site the odds are currently 3.3. This is a value bet as the odds are set higher to what they should be.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This is just one simple example of a value bet, unfortunly they won&#39;t always be like this.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>How to workout the actual probability?&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Firstly no one can give you the exact percentage of a team winning or both teams scoring ect.. However with in depth research you can come up with your own caluclaitons find out the probability that way. The four main things that should be taken into account are:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Home stats, overal stats for home team&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Away stats and overal stats for away team</li>\r\n	<li>H2h meetings&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Recent form&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>We infact have a little prediction tool on most fixtures, this gives you the percetnage of the team to win. Whilst it&#39;s not 100% accurate it takes all the things mentioned above into account. I reccomend you do your own research too and use the prediction tool as just a guide.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '2c9432e9e003637ec5dad5eb5a29b105.PNG', '', 0, 0, NULL, '2022-06-30 04:56:55', '2022-06-30 08:51:26', 0),
