(522, 'Football-today How likely both teams will score', NULL, '<hr />\r\n<p>Introduction:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The likelihood of both teams scoring in a football (soccer) match can vary widely based on a number of factors, including the teams&#39; playing styles, their attacking and defensive capabilities, the skill of the players, the tactics set by their manager&nbsp;and even external factors like weather conditions and home advantage.&nbsp;In general, matches between teams with strong attacking&nbsp;abilities and relatively weaker defenses are more likely to result in both teams scoring. Conversely, matches between defensively strong teams might be less likely to see both teams score. However, football is an unpredictable sport, and even matches that seem lopsided on paper can yield unexpected outcomes.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>What teams to look out for?&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '8e961e23a57ae4b15bc39d8137fd8995.png', '', 0, 0, 18, '2023-08-07 12:26:05', '2023-08-10 05:23:05', 0),
