(667, 'Both teams to score Betting strategy - Risk level high.', NULL, '<p><big><strong>Introduction</strong></big></p>\r\n\r\n<p>In this article we explain to you just one of the strategy that we use with the new BTTS predictions. It is a risky strategy but can be a very rewarding one.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p><big><strong>Strategy:</strong></big></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Firstly, You will need to&nbsp;open up a bookies/odds checker website/Betting exchange website. Ideally, an odds checker or exchange market so you can see the bests odds available.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Secondly, Look for games where the odds for BTTS YES is greater then 2.0 (Evens) and make a note of them games.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Next, head over to livefootballtoday.co.uk/favourtie-leagues&nbsp;and look for these games.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Once you find these games if the prediction for BTTS is YES click on the match and take a quick look at the forms and stats. If you think there is value in them odds then make a note of that game.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><big><strong>How we play these bets:</strong></big></p>\r\n\r\n<p>We place these as doubles with the odds for a double will being minium 4.00 +, for this example we will use 4.30:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>If you&#39;re using stakes of &pound;10.00 and place 10 doubles the total stake is &pound;100.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>If one of these doubles land you will make a profit of &pound;33.00 but your total return will be &pound;43.00&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Therefore, you will need just 3 of these doubles to win. 43 x 3 = 129. to make some profit.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>The profit would only be &pound;29.00 in this example, but with a win rate of just 30% required, it&#39;s very good. As long as 3 bets land per 10 bets you will be in profit.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Some weeks, you may get 4-6 winners and make 3 figures which is very possible. Other weeks you will make a small loss. But the profit is larger than the losses.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>I<strong>t is a risky strategy that requires good decision making and planning.</strong> These are fun to play and can be very rewarding, but do expect to make a loss some weeks. If the losses are greater and you don&#39;t make a profit then i would advise you to stop. Below are some top tips on how to pick the games:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Only pick the games that have BTTS YES</li>\r\n	<li>Secondly, check the form if they are scoring and conceding plenty then thats a good sign</li>\r\n	<li>Check the team stats, if one side has conceded an average of 0.4 goals per game, and the opposition averages 0.5 goals per game then it might not be worth the risk</li>\r\n	<li>Instead, look for games where each teams scores and conceded a minimum of 0.8 goals per game. Ideally anything over 1.0 but this won&#39;t always be the case.&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>That being said, If one team concedes an average of 0.7 &nbsp;but the opposition scores an average of 1.5 +&nbsp;goals then I would take this risk on this occasion as the opponents is a high scoring side. How much profit you make goes on your decision making.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p><big><strong>Conclusion</strong></big></p>\r\n\r\n<p>We recommend you stake only what you can afford to lose and if you&#39;re having no luck then please do stop before you make a big loss. The strategy isn&#39;t for everyone, but if you get it right it is indeed very rewarding.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'bb351ac127f570be76ecf0591b953309.png', 'paid', 0, 0, 24, '2024-02-19 13:36:14', '2024-02-19 16:39:42', 1),
