\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p><big><strong>Conclusion:</strong></big></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Wins are very important right now, so we have played all four predictions as singles, staking the same on each. We need three off these too land to make a profit. More you stake, more profit you can make of course. We&#39;ve also played this as a four fold staking a smaller amount as well as a small dobule with the first two selections.&nbsp;So regardless, we just need 3 wins to end the day in profit. We&#39;d like to apologise for this bad run, but these months do happen unfortunately.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '21ea0c5c972d5a6449fb98849eaa81e1.png', 'paid', 0, 0, 19, '2024-02-26 09:14:18', '2024-02-26 09:42:06', 1),
(683, 'LFT - Four fold betting strategy', NULL, '<p><big><strong>Introduction:</strong></big></p>\r\n\r\n<p>In this article we explore how another betting strategy that we do. It&#39;s. safe way of playing a four fold. We also play all games as singles and even if three singles land we will make a profit.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p><big><strong>The thinking behind this strategy:</strong></big></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Now you may ask what is the point of placing four singes, why not just place the four fold? Well, you can but ask yourself this, how many times has one selection let down your four fold? For me, in our 90% of the four folds that fail to land, I am let down by just ONE selection. This is why now, I play all the selections as singles to be safe and even if three off these singles land I&nbsp;make a small profit which is far better then losses. When all four singles and the&nbsp;fourfold land we can make three figures. (depending on your stakes)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You can do this on a weekly basis by picking four selections that you&#39;re most confident in that spread over the course of the week or you can do this as often as possible. It&#39;s advised to not overdo this as you risk getting carried away.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><big><strong>The strategy.&nbsp;</strong></big></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Find four selections with odds off at least 1.40</li>\r\n	<li>Stake the same amount on each singles&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Workout how much profit you can make with 3 singles landing and decide on your stake for the four fold. (Usually between 5-20% leaving you in profit if the three singles land)</li>\r\n	<li>Finally place the fourfold with the stake you&#39;re happy with. Make sure to keep track off these bets.&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Calculations - Using low odds</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"background:#eeeeee; border:1px solid #cccccc; padding:5px 10px\">Bet 1 =&nbsp; Stake: &pound;100 - Returns &pound;140 - Profit = &pound;40&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"background:#eeeeee; border:1px solid #cccccc; padding:5px 10px\">Bet 2 = Stake: &pound;100 - Returns 145 - Profit =&nbsp;&pound;45&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"background:#eeeeee; border:1px solid #cccccc; padding:5px 10px\">Bet 3 Stake: &pound;100&nbsp;- Returns &pound;140 - Loss = &pound;100</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"background:#eeeeee; border:1px solid #cccccc; padding:5px 10px\">Bet 4 = Stake: &pound;100&nbsp;Returns &pound;142 = Profit &pound;42</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"background:#eeeeee; border:1px solid #cccccc; padding:5px 10px\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"background:#eeeeee; border:1px solid #cccccc; padding:5px 10px\">Total stake &pound;400</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"background:#eeeeee; border:1px solid #cccccc; padding:5px 10px\">Total returned: 427</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"background:#eeeeee; border:1px solid #cccccc; padding:5px 10px\">Profit &pound;27.00&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<p>Not a huge profit by any means, but it&#39;s a good way of building a bank roll and a safer way or placing four fold bets. Using the example above, You could&#39;ve staked a further &pound;10.00 on an four fold and&nbsp; if the fourth selection landed as well as the four fold you would&#39;ve&nbsp;made &pound;200.00 +</p>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"background:#eeeeee; border:1px solid #cccccc; padding:5px 10px\">Total stake: &pound;410</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"background:#eeeeee; border:1px solid #cccccc; padding:5px 10px\">Total return without four fold: - 567</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"background:#eeeeee; border:1px solid #cccccc; padding:5px 10px\">Total profit without four fold - &pound;167</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"background:#eeeeee; border:1px solid #cccccc; padding:5px 10px\">Four fold returned - &pound;40</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"background:#eeeeee; border:1px solid #cccccc; padding:5px 10px\">Four fold profit - &pound;30</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"background:#eeeeee; border:1px solid #cccccc; padding:5px 10px\">Total profit &pound;200+&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><big><strong>What to look out for:</strong></big></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Of course, there&#39;s a risk of losing money and this strategy might not work for you. But, if you&#39;re like me where 90% of your four folds lose by just 1 selection then it&#39;s a great way to profit from this and potentially make 3-4 four figures a year. It&#39;s highly recommended that you shop around for best odds and to change your bookies often. If you can use betting exchanges to play most of your singles then this will be beneficial.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Example of using slightly higher odds:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"background:#eeeeee; border:1px solid #cccccc; padding:5px 10px\">Stake &pound;100 - Return &pound;155= Profit = &pound;55</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"background:#eeeeee; border:1px solid #cccccc; padding:5px 10px\">Stake &pound;100 - Returns 160 - Profit = &pound;60</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"background:#eeeeee; border:1px solid #cccccc; padding:5px 10px\">Stake &pound;100 - Returns &pound;168 = Loss</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"background:#eeeeee; border:1px solid #cccccc; padding:5px 10px\">Stake &pound;100 - Returns = 170 - Profit = &pound;70</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"background:#eeeeee; border:1px solid #cccccc; padding:5px 10px\">Total stake:&nbsp; &pound;400</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"background:#eeeeee; border:1px solid #cccccc; padding:5px 10px\">Total returned &pound;485</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"background:#eeeeee; border:1px solid #cccccc; padding:5px 10px\">Total profit &pound;85</div>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>With all four singles landing and the four fold using just &pound;10.00 stake for the fourfold</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"background:#eeeeee; border:1px solid #cccccc; padding:5px 10px\">Total stake - 410</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"background:#eeeeee; border:1px solid #cccccc; padding:5px 10px\">Total return from four fold - &pound;653</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"background:#eeeeee; border:1px solid #cccccc; padding:5px 10px\">Total profit from four fold - &pound;253</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"background:#eeeeee; border:1px solid #cccccc; padding:5px 10px\">Four fold total return - &pound;70</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"background:#eeeeee; border:1px solid #cccccc; padding:5px 10px\">Profit from four fold &pound;60</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"background:#eeeeee; border:1px solid #cccccc; padding:5px 10px\">Total profit = &pound;313</div>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p><big><strong>Conclusion:</strong></big></p>\r\n\r\n<p>These singles are a safe option of minimising losses. We do aim to land the four folds and do regularly which maximises profits. Please stake sensibly. If you have odds greater then 1.40, you will make even more profit. Try to use selections you&#39;re most confident&nbsp;rather then going by the odds, just make sure it&#39;s above 1.40.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '6c3b481bef36e47f7efc72eb9b37c5b2.png', 'paid', 0, 0, 24, '2024-02-26 10:54:39', '2024-02-26 11:10:03', 1),
