ber, genuine expertise and transparency are the hallmarks of trustworthy tipsters, so choose wisely and bet responsibly. Please feel free to ask us if you&#39;re unsure.</p>', '12d07c6980f6f42d6298ed57e134d838.png', 'free', 0, 0, 23, '2024-04-15 17:48:49', '2024-04-15 17:50:51', 1),
