 for a high-scoring affair and the unpredictable nature of finals, a safe bet would be to anticipate three or more goals, so my final prediction is Over 2.5 goals.</p>', '70aeffbf28782726b1f7257eefa00453.jpg', 'free', 0, 0, 19, '2024-05-13 14:02:28', '2024-05-13 14:02:28', 1),
